data.value:
Welcome to QUASAR!
1. Place your bet, you begin with 500 points.
2. Roll either the 1-8 or the 4-7 die, your goal is to get your sum as close to as possible 20 without going over.
3. Once your sum reaches 15 or over, you will have the option to stop rolling.
4. You have five rounds to maximize your profits!
